Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:37.07,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\fad(0,300)}在我的墓前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:43.35,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\fad(300,300)}请不要哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:49.29,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\fad(300,300)}我不在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:54.36,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\fad(300,300)}并没有就此沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:22:00.60,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\fad(300,300)}千风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:07.64,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\fad(300,300)}化作千风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:13.91,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\fad(300,300)}在宽广的天空中
